<paragraph id="8B8A36F1FFC3C234FDB9B823FE5E0C6F" blockId="19.[151,496,1798,1857]" box="[151,389,1833,1857]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">
(
<figureCitation id="130E2A74FFC3C234FDB1B823FF280C6F" box="[159,243,1833,1857]" captionStart="FIGURE 19. M" captionStartId="22.[151,250,1917,1940]" captionTargetBox="[244,1339,939,1868]" captionTargetId="figure@22.[188,1398,913,1896]" captionTargetPageId="22" captionText="FIGURE 19. M. pileiformis sp. nov. A: male pygofer lobe, lateral view; B: valve, ventral view; C: subgenital plate, ventral view; D: style, dorsal view; E &amp; F: aedeagus and connective, dorsal and lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/206134/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">
Fig. 
<number id="3DFD24D6FFC3C234FDFAB823FF280C6F" box="[212,243,1833,1857]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20" value="19.0">19</number>
</figureCitation>
; Plate IV: G)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8A36F1FFC3C234FDB9B87BFE490CA7" blockId="19.[151,1436,1905,2038]" box="[151,402,1905,1929]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">
Length. Male: 
<quantity id="4CCD9B14FFC3C234FC12B87BFE550CA7" box="[316,398,1905,1929]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.6" pageId="19" pageNumber="20" unit="mm" value="2.6">2.6mm</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8A36F1FFC3C234FDEBB89FFADA0CDB" blockId="19.[151,1436,1905,2038]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">Ochraceous. Vertex with sinuate oblique line on either side of median line on antero-lateral margin, patch on either side of median line (Plate IV: G). Pronotum with three longitudinal stripes on either side of median line (Plate IV: G). Basal triangles on scutellum orange (Plate IV: G). Forewing veins margined by brown.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8A36F1FFC4C233FDEBBF9DFCB10B81" blockId="20.[151,1436,151,464]" box="[197,874,151,175]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Forewing macropterous, inner anteapical cell closed basally.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C32F657AFFC4C233FDEBBFB6FA8C0A32" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" type="description">
<paragraph id="8B8A36F1FFC4C233FDEBBFB6FA8C0A32" blockId="20.[151,1436,151,464]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">
<emphasis id="B941EAE3FFC4C233FDEBBFB6FEA20BFA" bold="true" box="[197,377,187,212]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Male genitalia.</emphasis>
Subgenital plate subtriangular, apex acute (
<figureCitation id="130E2A74FFC4C233FE5CBFB6FC1D0BFA" box="[882,966,188,212]" captionStart="FIGURE 19. M" captionStartId="22.[151,250,1917,1940]" captionTargetBox="[244,1339,939,1868]" captionTargetId="figure@22.[188,1398,913,1896]" captionTargetPageId="22" captionText="FIGURE 19. M. pileiformis sp. nov. A: male pygofer lobe, lateral view; B: valve, ventral view; C: subgenital plate, ventral view; D: style, dorsal view; E &amp; F: aedeagus and connective, dorsal and lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/206134/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">
Fig. 
<number id="3DFD24D6FFC4C233FE87BFB6FC1D0BFA" box="[937,966,188,212]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" value="19.0">19</number>
</figureCitation>
C); style, preapical lobe short and broad, apophysis short and slim, digitate, slightly laterally curved (
<figureCitation id="130E2A74FFC4C233FE67BFD5FC460BD9" box="[841,925,223,247]" captionStart="FIGURE 19. M" captionStartId="22.[151,250,1917,1940]" captionTargetBox="[244,1339,939,1868]" captionTargetId="figure@22.[188,1398,913,1896]" captionTargetPageId="22" captionText="FIGURE 19. M. pileiformis sp. nov. A: male pygofer lobe, lateral view; B: valve, ventral view; C: subgenital plate, ventral view; D: style, dorsal view; E &amp; F: aedeagus and connective, dorsal and lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/206134/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">
Fig. 
<number id="3DFD24D6FFC4C233FEAEBFD5FC460BD9" box="[896,925,223,247]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" value="19.0">19</number>
</figureCitation>
D); aedeagal shaft tapering to apex in dorsal view, apex slightly curved dorsally, with ventral triangular membranous area in lateral view (
<figureCitation id="130E2A74FFC4C233F989BE0EFB270A32" box="[1191,1276,260,284]" captionStart="FIGURE 19. M" captionStartId="22.[151,250,1917,1940]" captionTargetBox="[244,1339,939,1868]" captionTargetId="figure@22.[188,1398,913,1896]" captionTargetPageId="22" captionText="FIGURE 19. M. pileiformis sp. nov. A: male pygofer lobe, lateral view; B: valve, ventral view; C: subgenital plate, ventral view; D: style, dorsal view; E &amp; F: aedeagus and connective, dorsal and lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/206134/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">
Figs 
<number id="3DFD24D6FFC4C233F9CEBE0EFB270A32" box="[1248,1276,260,284]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" value="19.0">19</number>
</figureCitation>
E, 
<number id="3DFD24D6FFC4C233F835BE0EFAE30A32" box="[1307,1336,260,284]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" value="19.0">19</number>
F).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
